ert, Jack</span>'''[[Jack Lambert (American football)|Jack Lambert]]''' || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1990 || [[Linebacker|LB]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{Steelers season|1974}}\u2013{{Steelers season|1984}}||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.profootballhof.com/hof/member.jsp?player_id=118|title=Jack Lambert \u2013 Pro Football Hall of Fame Official Site|website=www.profootballhof.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 22 ||<span style=\"display:none\">Layne, Bobby</span>'''[[Bobby Layne]]''' || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 1967 || [[Quarterback|QB]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{Steelers season|1958}}\u2013{{Steelers season|1962}} ||<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.profootballhof.com/hof/member.jsp?player_id=126|title=Bobby Layne \u2013 Pro Football Hall of Fame Official Site|website=www.profootballhof.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 43 ||<span style=\"display:none\">Polamalu, Troy</span>'''[[Troy Polamalu]]''' || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2020 || [[Safety (gridiron football position)|S]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{Steelers season|2003}}\u2013{{Steelers season|2014}} ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.profootballhof.com/five-modern-era-players-elected-to-hall-of-fame/|title=Five Modern-Era Players Elected to Hall of Fame|website=www.profootballhof.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 31 ||<span style=\"display:none\">Shell, Donnie</span>'''[[Donnie Shell]]''' || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2020 || [[Safety (gridiron football position)|S]] || style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{Steelers season|1974}}\u2013{{Steelers season|1987}} ||<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.profootballhof.com/centennial-slate-for-class-of-2020-revealed/|title=Centennial Slate for Class of 2020 Revealed|website=www.profootballhof.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 82 ||<span style=\"display:none\">Stallworth, John</span>'''[[John Stallworth]]''' || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 2002 || [[Wide receiver|WR]] || style=\"text